diff --git a/tokio/CHANGELOG.md b/tokio/CHANGELOG.md
index d2cb6a20..2155f14e 100644
--- a/tokio/CHANGELOG.md
+++ b/tokio/CHANGELOG.md
@@ -1,3 +1,17 @@
+# 1.43.1 (April 2nd, 2025)
+
+This release fixes a soundness issue in the broadcast channel. The channel
+accepts values that are `Send` but `!Sync`. Previously, the channel called
+`clone()` on these values without synchronizing. This release fixes the channel
+by synchronizing calls to `.clone()` (Thanks Austin Bonander for finding and
+reporting the issue).
+
+### Fixed
+
+- sync: synchronize `clone()` call in broadcast channel ([#7232])
+
+[#7232]: https://github.com/tokio-rs/tokio/pull/7232
+
 # 1.43.0 (Jan 8th, 2025)
 
 ### Added
@@ -303,6 +317,20 @@ Yanked. Please use 1.39.1 instead.
 [#6709]: https://github.com/tokio-rs/tokio/pull/6709
 [#6710]: https://github.com/tokio-rs/tokio/pull/6710
 
+# 1.38.2 (April 2nd, 2025)
+
+This release fixes a soundness issue in the broadcast channel. The channel
+accepts values that are `Send` but `!Sync`. Previously, the channel called
+`clone()` on these values without synchronizing. This release fixes the channel
+by synchronizing calls to `.clone()` (Thanks Austin Bonander for finding and
+reporting the issue).
+
+### Fixed
+
+- sync: synchronize `clone()` call in broadcast channel ([#7232])
+
+[#7232]: https://github.com/tokio-rs/tokio/pull/7232
+
